"[00:01:33] Extracting src... done\n"
"[00:02:31] Fetching lib32 for FreeBSD 13.1-RELEASE amd64\n"
"/poudriere/jails/13amd64/fromftp/lib32.txz              24 MB 3969 kBps    06s\n"
"[00:02:38] Extracting lib32... done\n"
